title: Andrew Sheets: The Risk of Rising Rates
description: Whether the anticipated fiscal stimulus in the U.S. will be enough to push the economy into inflationary territory, and if we should be concerned about it, is a matter of much debate. Chief Cross-Asset Strategist Andrew Sheets discusses.
